text: Ahmetović () is a Bosniak surname, a patronymic derived from the given name Ahmet. Notable people with the surname include: *Denial Ahmetović (born 1995), Bosnian singer *Denis Ahmetović (born 1995), Serbian footballer *Esmir Ahmetović (born 1991), Bosnian footballer *Mersudin Ahmetović (born 1985), Bosnian footballer ==See also== *Ahmedović *Ahmetić *Ahmetlić *Ahmedovski *Ahmić Category:Bosnian-language surnames Category:Serbian-language surnames Category:Patronymic surnames
title: Ahmetović
